24#include <sys/cdefs.h>
25__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_fb_gk20a.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:33 riastradh Exp $");
26
27#include "priv.h"
28
29static void
30gk20a_fb_init(struct nvkm_fb *fb)
31{
32 struct nvkm_device *device = fb->subdev.device;
33 nvkm_mask(device, 0x100c80, 0x00000001, 0x00000000); /* 128KiB lpg */
34}
35
36static const struct nvkm_fb_func
37gk20a_fb = {
38 .init = gk20a_fb_init,
39 .memtype_valid = gf100_fb_memtype_valid,
40};
41
42int
43gk20a_fb_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index, struct nvkm_fb **pfb)
44{
45 return nvkm_fb_new_(&gk20a_fb, device, index, pfb);
46}
